data.description: Welcome to your beautifully remodeled two-story home in the highly sought-after Park Field neighborhood of Denver!  Located at 15619 E 51st Dr, this residence offers three spacious bedrooms, three modern bathrooms, & the convenience of a one-car garage. With a tasteful renovation & thoughtful upgrades, this home is ready to provide comfort, style, & convenience to its new owners. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail that went into transforming this house into a warm & inviting home. The main floor boasts an open concept design, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, & kitchen. The living space is bathed in natural light, creating a bright & airy atmosphere. The chef's kitchen is a true highlight, featuring a suite of high-end stainless steel appliances that are included with the property. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply enjoy cooking for your loved ones, this kitchen is sure to delight. The ample cabinet & countertop space provide both functionality & aesthetics. Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, each offering its own unique charm. The master bedroom, complete with an en-suite bathroom, provides a tranquil retreat for rest & relaxation. The en-suite bathroom features modern fixtures & finishes, creating a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home. Perfectly situated for those who value convenience. Its proximity to major highways ensures quick & easy access to Denver's vibrant downtown & surrounding areas. The beautiful backyard is like an oasis with a shed that's perfect for storage. Additionally, you'll find shopping centers, restaurants, & entertainment options just a stone's throw away, making it easy to enjoy all that Denver has to offer. Blocks away from the park, schools and recreation center. Solar panels can be leased, huge savings! Don't miss your chance to make this house your new home; schedule a viewing today & discover the lifestyle that awaits you!
